text: <@U2670DYLE> such an awesome idea, just sent it to an artist friend of mine who is psyched to submit
Thank you, and thank you for spreading the word!

I spoke with Jared Weiner from PDC today about our Civic Action goals and energy. He’s still on paternity leave but mentioned that there’s an RFP coming from the city that might be worth applying for.
It’s not directly tied to this but it could be an opportunity for us to get some money from the city.

Additionally, he mentioned sharing some insights for progressive concepts that their group developed a couple years ago but haven’t put into action - anything from parking to redistricting. Might be helpful research fodder for future explorations.
If nothing else, we have an advocate for us at the city level.
